### Get Tenant Details
GET /tenants/1 HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8081
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here

### List All Tenants for Current User
GET /tenants HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8081
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here

### Switch to a Different Tenant
POST /tenants/switch HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8081
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenant_id": 2
}

### Set Default Tenant
POST /tenants/default HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8081
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenant_id": 1
}

### Add User to Tenant
POST /tenants/users HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8081
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tenant_id": 1,
  "user_email": "newuser@example.com",
  "role": "member"
}

### Remove User from Tenant
DELETE /tenants/1/users/2 HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8081
Authorization: Bearer your_jwt_token_here

### Login with Tenant Context
POST /auth/login HTTP/1.1
Host: localhost:8081
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "tenant_id": 1
}